Subject: [PATCH v3 2/2] hwmon: Add "label" attribute
Date:   Mon, 10 Jan 2022 18:22:56 +0000
Message-Id: <20220110182256.30763-3-paul@crapouillou.net>
In-Reply-To: <20220110182256.30763-1-paul@crapouillou.net>
